
############################ USER ############################
### Inscription
POST http://localhost:4001/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"userName": "yohan",
	"email": "yo@example.com",
	"password": "123456"
}

### Connexion
POST http://localhost:4001/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "yo@example.com",
	"password": "123456"
}

### Accéder au profil (JWT requis)
GET http://localhost:4001/user/profile
Authorization: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc0MTI3MDQyMH0.-BOy3HcAD8BDZNjWtmzYeZDKgO3d9Q5UtMVWQ_zznDQ

