############################ GAME ############################

### Start game
POST http://localhost:4002/game/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"player1_id": 1,
	"player2_id": 2
}


### Get game
GET http://localhost:4002/game/1


### Update Score
PUT http://localhost:4002/game/1/score
Content-Type: application/json

{"score1": 2, "score2": 3}

### End Game
POST http://localhost:4002/game/1/end
